# Learned while inputting big number

After learning how to input and output in C, I tried to input a big number in the next code.

~~~C
#include <stdio.h>

int main(void)
{
  {
      int input;
      printf("input a number\n");
      scanf("%d", &input);
      printf("input number : %d\n",input);
    }
  return 0;
}
~~~


